    "body": "I've found [an issue](https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/11593) indicates `abi.encodePacked` is not recommended. It's not standardized, only use the minimal required memory to encode the data and maybe can not be decoded. The abi encode implementation of `go-etheruem` are same as `abi.encode` in solidity. \r\n\r\nIt's not a bug. And I will use more standardized methods. :-)\r\n",
